name: Shohreh Aghdashloo
description:
A commission of @Zorglub.

Shohreh Aghdashloo is an Iranian/American actress, mainly known for her role in the sci-fi TV show The Expanse.

Updated: Apologies for the quick update, but I misjudged step 1200 at first and it seems actually better than the previous version. :)

1200-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images with my usual settings.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

How to create a good prompt using my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (sh0hreh:0.99), a woman, closeup zoomed in tight crop portrait, sitting at a (table on a seaside boardwalk cafe bar drinks cocktails:1.2) wearing a (sexy sweater off-shoulders:1.3) (drinks on table:1.3) (Lighting-Gold:1.2) foreground objects background details (masterpiece:1.2) (photorealistic:1.2) (bokeh:1.2) (best quality) (color grading) (detailed skin:1.3) (intricate) (8k) (HDR) (cinematic lighting:1.3) (sharp focus)"
